

■ hyperlink: 
referring url
//<a href="https://www.wikipedia.org" target="_blank">Visit Wikipedia</a>

referring repository address
//<a href="_posts/photo.png">View the photo</a>


■ attach the image
In this webpage, it seems only works with the repository folder address.
you can find the path of the file if you see next to file name after [caragim.github.io/] part.

example:
//<img src="_posts/photo.png" alt="My photo">

